history.content: 162 will make you the most recruitable programmer as far as CS classes at Cal go. Prioritize that if recruitment is your focus. 162 also teaches the most ubiquitous set of skills you will use in practically any subfield of software/EE/CS. 164 and 184 would also teach good programming skills but are definitely more focused in scope. Same goes for 161/186 but they are not as intense as the other 3.
